					</ul>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="copyrights wrapper">
			Copyright Â© 2015 <a href="http://pixelhint.com" target="_blank" class="ph_link" title="Download more free Templates">Pixelhint.com</a>. All Rights Reserved.
